Stop (script event)
===================

Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [Game\_class.html game class] type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Stops a func\_camera\_anim if it was playing an [MD5ANIM\_(file\_format).html MD5Anim] file.

Usage
-----

*void* stop( )

Parameters
----------

None.

Examples
--------

<font color="#000055">`$mycamera`</font>`.`<font color="#ff0000">`stop`</font><font color="#000000">`(`</font><font color="#000000">`)`</font>

Notes
-----

This script event does not return any values.


